/*

# Explicitly track these directories
!/.github/
!/kb/
!/.gitignore
!/SIE/

# =============================================================================
# SIE AGENT LOOP
# =============================================================================

# 1. Allow the directory structure leading to the agent

!/SIE/
!/SIE/04_Engine/
!/SIE/04_Engine/sie-agent-loop/

# 2. Re-ignore everything inside SIE EXCEPT the 04_Engine folder

/SIE/*
!/SIE/04_Engine/

# 3. Re-ignore everything inside 04_Engine EXCEPT the sie-agent-loop folder

/SIE/04_Engine/*
!/SIE/04_Engine/sie-agent-loop/

# 4. Final safety: Block the heavy environment and secrets inside the agent folder

SIE/04_Engine/sie-agent-loop/.venv/
SIE/04_Engine/sie-agent-loop/.env
SIE/04_Engine/sie-agent-loop/pycache/

